{"tid":1082588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"躁男Band房狂掟樽　退房扮冇事：倒瀉少少水","createTime":"2019-03-29T05:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T07:29:09.000Z","uid":225464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bde1d4bc6192478ecd923678a5909123ee482188","tid":1082588,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:10:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>躁男Band房狂掟樽 退房扮冇事：倒瀉少少水</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UgMa0h\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UgMa0h&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HRY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=e3e263d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UgMa0h</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190329125422\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190329125422&h=3932d78c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無啦啦喺Band房鬧交？<br />\n<br />\n曾有港女到台灣搗亂民宿扮無事，引起全城關注，到底港人公德水準有幾高？近日一對男女租用樂隊練習室時疑離奇「扯火」，男方多次激動掟水樽弄濕設備，令場主大感無奈！<br />\n<br />\n該場主周三（27日）在社交媒體專頁發貼，指有一男一女客人租用Band房時，不但逾時交還房間，還向職員表示：「唔好意思，倒瀉咗少少水」，然後默默離去。<br />\n<br />\n貼文寫道:「打翻飲料／留下食物碎屑也不是罕見的事，本來櫃枱職員也是打算於客人離開後自行到房間自行清理，可是一打開房門，就發現不但地面有大面積的水灘，房中的結他，Amplifier（音箱）亦完全濕透至內部。」<br />\n<br />\n職員翻查閉路電視，發現該男子3次將手上水樽用力擲向女友人方向，以致弄濕音響設備，「我們的設備都不是最高級的最貴的東西，但每一件都是用辛勞血汗錢買來，就是希望為喜歡音樂的朋友提供一個地方&hellip;但每每發生這類型的事件時，都會不禁令我們問『繼續做下去，真的值得嗎？』」<br />\n<br />\n他續說：「再熱血的『火』，也會有熄滅的一天，當你借了別人的設備，並沒有妥善使用，下一個想跟朋友分享音樂的朋友，就可能因此失去一個機會了」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網友質疑該對男女：「似鬧交多於玩樂器」、「3次唔會係冇心啦」，有人認為：「你哋（場地公司）唔報警係助長惡行」、「有片證明到係刻意破壞一定要報」，又建議：「每次客走之前，要有職員驗收間房先畀佢走」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190329125422\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190329125422&h=612c7ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子多次將水樽（紅圈示）大力扔去地下。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190329125422\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190329125422&h=e0091b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n掉完再掉。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_05p.jpg?20190329125422\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20190329125422&h=503449d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂器也沾濕。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_06p.jpg?20190329125422\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20190329125422&h=082ae0fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連音箱都濕了。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190329/photo/bkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190329125422\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190329114621180-0329_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190329125422&h=d1112cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事後地板有水漬。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"7cf7ecc8adec1c7d536ad987d72abecf11b8b8c8","tid":1082588,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:14:00.000Z","msg":"按金咪得囉<br />\n你話夠唔夠賠呢，就一定唔夠<br />\n但都唔會俾佢拍下屎忽就走左去"},{"pid":"72bdd4b8b8d1547fa8bc0c1d00fcf785b9a8ecf5","tid":1082588,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"租band房嗌交 貪有隔音？"},{"pid":"389a47ba183bcbc55fb826ebd5efc7028d788077","tid":1082588,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":